  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180°C. In a large bowl, combine the rest-meat, onion, scotch bonnet peppers, flour, baking powder, and salt. Mix well until the dry ingredients are evenly distributed.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix the worcestershire sauce, vegetable oil, plant-based milk, molasses, brown sugar, and soy sauce. Add this mixture to the dry ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a greased 20cm x 20cm baking dish and smooth the top.",
    "Bake for 45 minutes or until the top is golden brown and the rest-meat is cooked through."
  ],
